root: ^Phew... Feels like I barely made it through today...
^(The portal activates, and O'Ryan steps through.)
^(They hand out my envelope, and I stuff it in my pocket)
^Thanks... Just gotta finish cleaning up, and everything should be all set.
^(O'Ryan nods, turns, and leaves the diner through the portal.)
^Alright... I still got a lotta cleaning to do...
